81.title: Jung -2
81.plot: Sameer is rescued by the police from getting murdered. A terrified Sameer then tells the story about how he was brainwashed and convinced to join forces with the Jihadi, by a girl named Cynthia. The police now start their search to find the person who is responsible for brainwashing people like Sameer, and turn them into Jihadis.

82.title: Naata
82.plot: This episode tells the story about Kajal, a murderer from Rajasthan, who seduces men, and later after their marriage, she kills them and runs away with their money. When the police investigate the case, they discover that Kajal is being forced by someone to commit those crimes. Will the police find out the real culprit?

83.title: Giraft
83.plot: This episode takes us to Gujarat, where people are tortured both physically and mentally, by a cruel extortionist. Scared of the consequences that await them if they fail to give him the huge sum of interest, people even end up killing their whole family and committing suicide. Who is this powerful person who compels his victims to give up their life? Will he be punished for his crimes?

84.title: Male Foeticide
84.plot: This episode tells the story about a case in New Mumbai, where young girls are forcefully kept, if they get pregnant while prostituting. If the fetus is discovered to be male during the sonography test, they forcefully abort it. As the police dig deeper into the case, they discover a long chain of culprits associated with this. Who are the real masterminds behind the act?

85.title: Lalach
85.plot: This episode takes us to Nasik where 7 years old Rohan suddenly goes missing from home. Rohan one day goes to tuition and never returns back. His parents approach the police but even they fail to track down Rohan. Later, kidnappers contact Rohan's parents and demand a huge sum for his release. Who are the kidnappers? Will the police succeed in rescuing Rohan from them?

86.title: Shatir
86.plot: A Mumbai resident, Lakshmi lives with her young granddaughter Sweety in an apartment. One of her neighbors, Sonu, gets extensively familiar with Lakshmi and Sweetie and one day he brutally murders both of them and escapes with all the wealth. Sonu leaves few clues to divert Police away from him and makes others fall as a prime suspect. How far will Sonu be able to save himself from the police?

87.title: Paheli
87.plot: The mysterious disappearance of the Gawit family, is soon followed by the discovery of the decapitated body of Sumitra Gawit. Soon, the Mumbai police discover the dead body of Pavan Gawit, who is also murdered in a vicious manner. With Archana Gawit still missing, will the police succeed in solving this mystery?

88.title: Paheli -2

Who is this woman, and why is she harboring hatred for Archana?
